subtopics.content:
Common Flexbox layout patterns.

**Center Content:**
```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
```

**Equal Width Columns:**
```css
.container {
  display: flex;
}
.item {
  flex: 1; /* All items equal width */
}
```

**Navigation Bar:**
```css
.nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
```

**Card Layout:**
```css
.card-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 20px;
}
.card {
  flex: 1 1 300px; /* Grow, shrink, basis */
}
```

CSS Grid is a two-dimensional layout system for rows and columns.

**Enabling Grid:**
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
}
```

**Grid Template:**
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; /* 3 equal columns */
  grid-template-rows: 100px 200px; /* 2 rows */
  gap: 20px; /* Gap between items */
}
```

**Grid Shorthand:**
```css
.container {
  grid-template: 
    'header header header'
    'sidebar main main'
    'footer footer footer';
}
```

Control where items are placed in the grid.

**Grid Lines:**
```css
.item {
  grid-column-start: 1;
  grid-column-end: 3;
  grid-row-start: 1;
  grid-row-end: 2;
}

/* Shorthand */
.item {
  grid-column: 1 / 3;
  grid-row: 1 / 2;
}

/* Span */
.item {
  grid-column: span 2; /* Span 2 columns */
  grid-row: span 1;
}
```

**Grid Areas:**
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-areas:
    'header header header'
    'sidebar main main'
    'footer footer footer';
}

.header { grid-area: header; }
.sidebar { grid-area: sidebar; }
.main { grid-area: main; }
.footer { grid-area: footer; }
```

Create responsive layouts that adapt to screen sizes.

**Responsive Flexbox:**
```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.item {
  flex: 1 1 300px; /* Basis 300px, can grow/shrink */
}

/* Media query */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
```

**Responsive Grid:**
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}

/* Alternative approach */
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
```
